{"tid":552739,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日本研究出新負極材料：可提升電池容量與壽命","createTime":"2018-02-06T22:05:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T22:10:50.000Z","uid":80108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6987d44a93d29a38731d856be8b732b612bdf709","tid":552739,"uid":80108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T22:05:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.pconline.com.cn/1081/10817667.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.pconline.com.cn%2F1081%2F10817667.html&d=BHXERQ%2Buve8Ngw6OonVBHqNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=c60423c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.pconline.com.cn/1081/10817667.html</a>"},{"pid":"176fccdc8fc4666b5a523d4bc649aec975782c24","tid":552739,"uid":80108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6987d44a93d29a38731d856be8b732b612bdf709","tid":552739,"uid":80108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T22:05:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.pconline.com.cn/1081/10817667.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.pconline.com.cn%2F1081%2F10817667.html&d=BHXERQ%2Buve8Ngw6OonVBHqNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=c60423c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.pconline.com.cn/1081/10817667.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T22:08:12.000Z","msg":"日本物質材料研究機構(NIMS)日前公布，他們的一個研究小組成功合成了氧化錳納米片和石墨烯交替重疊的材料，而這種新型負極材料可提高電池容量兩倍以上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據悉，該覆合材料作為鋰及鈉離子充電電池的負極材料，可將電池充放電容量提高兩倍以上，且能延長重覆使用壽命，或將可以解決現如今電池容量和壽命不可兼得的問題。<br />\n<br />\n研究小組在溶液中分散氧化錳納米片並與石墨烯混合，合成了交互多層的層壓覆合材料，而此次通過把兩種物質從分子水平覆合得到的覆合材料，得到了單獨材料難以實現的高特性。據悉，這種覆合材料除用於充電電池之外，還可大幅提高超級電容器、電極催化劑等能量儲存及轉換系統的效能。"},{"pid":"8529645c76792ff0078324bab748ed5987a47a8e","tid":552739,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T22:08:56.000Z","msg":"勁"},{"pid":"77f0c4dc66013a2bdc09ca93d2b07737e6127393","tid":552739,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T22:09:07.000Z","msg":"電話商：你班傻閪我一早有新科技買曬專利啦<br />\n你電唔壞我點賺錢丫？懵撚！"},{"pid":"1dce834b187231d6b761a2bb8135e2844ec84f39","tid":552739,"uid":83754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T22:10:50.000Z","msg":"年中唔少, 最後不了了之"}]}